  <brief_title>Patient Education Study to Determine Knowledge Acquisition in Patients Preparing to Undergo Lung Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>&quot;A Comparison of 2 Different Methods of Patient Education to Determine Knowledge Acquisition in Patients Preparing to Undergo Lung Transplantation&quot;</official_title>
  <sponsors>
