  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Lung Transplant Team at Tampa General Hospital has identified a need to improve both the
      quality and quantity of the education that is provided to patients listed for lung
      transplantation. We propose to change the method and timing of our transplant patient
      education. The objective of this prospective data collection will be to collect and analyze
      pre and post test scores of patients when patient education is provided via compact disc as
      compared to individualized teaching.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
